result.execSummary:
The defendant Tyrone Zeron Gibson Jr was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Tyrone Zeron Gibson Jr is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Tyrone Zeron Gibson Jr was found guilty of Burglary-Building or Dwelling, a class F felony, Wisconsin Statutes 943.10(1m)(a).
  • Tyrone Zeron Gibson Jr was found guilty of Theft-Movable Property <=$2500, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 943.20(1)(a).
  • Tyrone Zeron Gibson Jr was found guilty of Obstructing an Officer, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 946.41(1).
  • Tyrone Zeron Gibson Jr was found guilty of Bail Jumping-Felony, a class H felony, Wisconsin Statutes 946.49(1)(b).
  • Tyrone Zeron Gibson Jr was found guilty of Bail Jumping-Felony, a class H felony, Wisconsin Statutes 946.49(1)(b).
